---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContextAlert from '../components/ContextAlert.astro';
import Markdown from '../components/Markdown.astro';

const explainer = `

Minabocks has you covered from building a new website to SEO, digital advertising, and social media. 

Our team of digital experts are uniquely positioned to bring your digital dreams to reality. 
Our team, located throughout the United States and Europe, with a wide breadth of digital experience, is set to offer you a unique experience.
`;
---

<Layout title="Minabocks">
    <ContextAlert class="mb-8" />
    <h1 class="mb-10">A NextGen Digital Experience</h1>
    <p>
        <a href="https://calendly.com/kevinbrown-dc/minabocks" class="btn btn-lg sm:min-w-64">Book a Meeting</a>
        
    </p>
        <br>
    <Markdown content={explainer} class="mb-10 text-lg" />
<br>
<h2> What is a NextGen digital experience?</h2>
<p>ChatGPT said:

A NextGen digital experience isn’t just about technology—it’s about creating seamless, personalized, and intuitive interactions that delight users at every touchpoint. Imagine a digital ecosystem where AI anticipates your needs, data flows effortlessly across platforms, and every click feels faster, smarter, and more human. This is the power of NextGen: transforming static websites and clunky apps into immersive, adaptive journeys that keep customers engaged, loyal, and coming back for more. It’s not the future of digital—it’s the competitive advantage brands need today!</p>

</Layout>
